  "texts": [
    "While ML and automation are transforming this field, the indispensable role of human insight, creativity, and strategic thinking cannot be replaced.",
    "The most effective and innovative outcomes in materials synthesis will emerge from workflows that skillfully combine the strengths of both humans and machines.",
    "This integration is imperative because the reward functions, which drive workflow development, must originate from human objectives and goals.",
    "Additionally, humans can collaborate with AI in refining hypotheses and recognizing serendipitous experimental findings, a partnership that helps mitigate potential misalignments between ML-generated workflows and human intentions.",
    "This collaborative dynamic raises a compelling question: What is the optimal form of humanin-the-loop technology, tailored to human preferences and capabilities?"
  ],
